sectionHeading: Weekend Events / Traffic Impacts for August 14 - 15

day: Bridge Deck Overlay Work for I-75S at the Clays Ferry Bridge:
event: Currently in progress thru Labor Day weekend with work scheduled 24 hrs/day.  Two lanes will be closed and two lanes will remain open (including the shoulder).
